22/* Hash table entry. */
23struct gl_hash_entry
24{
25 struct gl_hash_entry *hash_next; /* chain of entries in same bucket */
26 size_t hashcode; /* cache of values' common hash code */
27};
28typedef struct gl_hash_entry * gl_hash_entry_t;
